snippet.title: Heavy Spoilers
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Heavy Spoilers show. Here we do breakdowns, reviews, recaps, easter egg hunts, ending explained videos and point out the things you missed in Marvel movies, Netflix TV Shows, DC Stuff and a lot more.

You probably want to know a bit about me.

As I was born the doctor walked in and said ‘Darth Vader is Luke’s father’

Just as he was doing it he spilled a bunch of chemicals on me

Fused with my body and his words I became the Spoilerman

Every day Monday to Sunday we talk about the biggest spoilers in movies, tv shows, games and more!

We've got a fantastic community here that's made up of hundreds of thousands of fantastic people just like you so if you wanna be in the know make sure you subscribe to the channel

Or follow us Twitter at - https://twitter.com/heavyspoilers
